<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1256</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lái ba xíng zǒu tiān lù de zhī tǐ ràng wǒ men yī tóng xié qǐ shǒu
 tuō lí shì jiè de wǎng luō jǐn gēn zhǔ yé sū
 shèng tú yào tuán jié yǒu ài xiāng hù fú zhù
 jǐng xǐng dǎo gào yì xiàng qīng chǔ xiàng qián jiù yǒu lù
 chóu dí bù néng jìn zhǐ wǒ men chéng wèi zhǔ de mén tú
 huán jìng bù néng lán zǔ wǒ men fú shì zhǔ de jiǎo bù
 shān lǐng suī gāo réng yào pān dēng zǒu biàn gè xiāng gè zú
 bǎ zhǔ de jiù ēn chuán yáng qīng chǔ wǒ men shì hé děng yǒu fú</lyrics>
<title>xíng zǒu tiān lù de zhī tǐ 迦南1256</title>
</song>